    "For each generative model a total of 100,000 synthetic 5-channel images were generated.",
    "For the GANs this took about 10 minutes, while it took 1.5 days (using 8 GPUs) for the diffusion model The synthetic images and the trained generative models are shared on AIDA data hub 44, 45.",
